  <brief_title>Analgesic Effects of Topical Ketamine Mouthwash in Patients Receiving Chemoradiation or Radiotherapy for Head and Neck Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analgesic Effects of Topical Ketamine Mouthwash in Patients Receiving Chemoradiation or Radiotherapy for Head and Neck Cancer</official_title>
